  {
    "id": 1286978,
    "position": 2,
    "description": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://instructure-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/account_74070000000000001/attachments/8409020/dp_app.css\"><p>Please consider who and when you were given strong career or personal advice, and the consequences to you of listening to or accepting that advice.</p>\n<p>Q: &nbsp;What is the absolute <strong><em>worst-ever advice</em></strong> you have ever been given and what was the result? &nbsp;</p>\n<p>On the whole, reflecting back on it, was it generally a positive or negative value to you?&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>NOTE FORMAT: </strong><span>&nbsp;Single-spaced, 1-2 page submission, 10-point Arial font with maximum 1\" margins.&nbsp;</span></p><script src=\"https://instructure-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/account_74070000000000001/attachments/8409019/dp_app.js\"></script>",
